caption:
Brentwood Elementary Science Magnet invites you to our 2nd Annual Community Resource Fair & Parent Engagement Workshop!

Date: Saturday, April 5th
Time: 10AM – 1PM
Location: 740 S. Gretna Green, Los Angeles, CA 90049

Bring the whole family out for:
	•	Carnival games
	•	Live DJ & fun activities
	•	Free food & giveaways
	•	Hands-on workshops for parents
	•	FREE clothes, diapers & essentials!
	•	Meet the staff & explore local resources

PLUS a special RELIEF Pop-Up for fire-impacted families! Bring proof (FEMA number, utility bill, etc.) to receive a FREE $100 Gift Card while supplies last.

Come connect, learn, and celebrate with your community!
